flowchart TD
    Start([User Presses<br/>Volume Down Button]) --> RC[Remote Control<br/>Sends BLE Command]
    RC --> HA{Connected to<br/>Hearing Aids?}
    HA -->|Yes - Single Device| HA1[Left/Right Hearing Aid<br/>Decreases Volume]
    HA -->|Yes - Dual Device| HA2[Both Hearing Aids<br/>Decrease Volume]
    HA -->|No| NoAction[No Action]
    HA1 --> Display[Display Shows<br/>New Volume Level]
    HA2 --> Display
    Display --> End([Complete])
    NoAction --> End
    
    style Start fill:#e1f5e1
    style End fill:#ffe1e1